rows.label: tlk45100141_03_msg0001
rows.name: What's going to happen to us all?

rows.label: tlk45100141_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Is Invidia going to be destroyed
too? Or even all of Alst?

rows.label: tlk45100141_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I don't want it to all be over yet... I
never even invented anything myself! I
want to be a scientist like my dad!

rows.label: tlk45100141_03_msg0004
rows.name:
There are so many things
I still want to do...

rows.label: tlk45100141_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Thanks. I'm counting on you
guys! Somehow I'm sure you can
save me, my dad...everybody!
